  93:Core/Src/audio_test.c ****     /*
  94:Core/Src/audio_test.c ****      * Important STM32 HAL I2S quirk:
  95:Core/Src/audio_test.c ****      *
  96:Core/Src/audio_test.c ****      * In 32-bit I2S mode, HAL_I2S_Transmit_DMA() expects the number
  97:Core/Src/audio_test.c ****      * of 32-bit audio samples, not the number of uint16_t halfwords.
