 102:Core/Src/audio_test.c ****      * For stereo:
 103:Core/Src/audio_test.c ****      * 480 frames × 2 channels = 960 32-bit samples.
 104:Core/Src/audio_test.c ****      * HAL turns that into 1920 halfword DMA transfers.
